---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Despre RAIDAVA — Povestea noastra">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-green-primary text-white py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Despre RAIDAVA</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-medium text-cream-dark">Povestea unei ferme nascute din viziune, curaj si pamant bun</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Povestea Fondatorului -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-green-primary mb-8 text-center">Povestea Fondatorului</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark">
        <div class="space-y-4 text-green-primary/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Drumul catre RAIDAVA a inceput cu o educatie diversa si neconventionala. Cu o baza in
            <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">electrica tehnica</span> si
            <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">administratie publica</span>, completata de
            <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">15 ani de experienta in hospitality</span>,
            fiecare etapa a construit o intelegere profunda a sistemelor complexe — cum functioneaza, cum se optimizeaza si cum se conduc.
          </p>
          <p>
            Decizia de a parasi Statele Unite si de a reveni in Romania, mai exact in
            <span class="font-semibold text-green-primary">Vulturesti, judetul Arges</span>,
            nu a fost o retragere — a fost o inaintare constienta. O alegere de a construi ceva durabil,
            ancorat in pamantul si traditia locului, dar ghidat de cunostinte moderne si gandire sistemica.
          </p>
          <p>
            RAIDAVA este rezultatul acestei convergente: disciplina din industria ospitalitatii,
            rigurozitatea tehnica si dorinta de a demonstra ca o ferma mica poate fi un sistem
            complet auto-sustenabil.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- De ce RAIDAVA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-green-primary mb-8 text-center">De ce RAIDAVA</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-green-secondary">
            <p class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-green-primary mb-1">RAI</p>
            <p class="text-green-primary/70">Din romanescul <span class="italic">rai</span> — paradis. Viziunea unui loc unde natura si omul traiesc in armonie deplina.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-brown-earth">
            <p class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-green-primary mb-1">DAVA</p>
            <p class="text-green-primary/70">Din dacicul <span class="italic">dava</span> — asezare fortificata. Simbol al rezistentei, al autonomiei si al radacinilor adanci in acest pamant.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-primary/5 border border-green-primary/20 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="font-heading text-4xl font-extrabold text-green-primary mb-3">RAIDAVA</p>
          <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-brown-earth mx-auto mb-3"></div>
          <p class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-green-secondary mb-2">Un paradis fortificat de hrana</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/60">O ferma care se hraneste singura, protejata de propria diversitate si rezilienta.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- De ce Vulturesti -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-green-primary mb-8 text-center">De ce Vulturesti</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-green-primary/70 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Locatia nu a fost aleasa intamplator. Vulturesti reuneste conditiile ideale pentru o ferma regenerativa.
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brown-earth/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brown-earth" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 21h18M3 21V7l9-4 9 4v14" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold mb-2">Sol Fertil Aluvial</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/60">Soluri aluviale in lunca, bogate in nutrienti, bine drenate — fundatia ideala pentru culturi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-secondary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold mb-2">734 mm/an</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/60">Precipitatii anuale suficiente pentru agricultura fara irigatie costisitoare.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-light/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold mb-2">65% Paduri</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/60">Acoperire forestiera bogata, biodiversitate naturala, microclimat protejat.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brown-light/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brown-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold mb-2">Traditie Pomicola</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-primary/60">Zona cu traditie agricola si pomicola puternica, climat temperat ideal pentru agricultura mixta.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
